### PNFS Manager
Historically, dCache namespace was allowing hard links on directories. This violates
POSIX restrictions and source of file system cyclic loops. With release dCache release 8.2
creation of hard links on directories is not allowed any more. The existing hard links will
work as before, however, recommended to be replace with soft links.

### Pool

Added `rm kill` command that canceles a pending file remove request from HSM.

### Poolmanager

PoolManager is update to support pool groups that contains other pool groups. For example:

```
psu create pgroup -dynamic -tags=hw-class=IO io-pools
psu create pgroup -dynamic -tags=hw-class=replica replica-pools
psu create pgroup all-pools
psu addto pgroup all-pools @io-pools @replica-pools
```

The values prefixed by `@` to `psu addto pgroup` command threaded as groups.

